https://www.packer.io/docs/builders/vmware/vsphere-clone
https://github.com/hashicorp/packer/tree/master/builder/vsphere/examples/
It uses the official vCenter API, and does not require ESXi host modification
This builder is supported for vSphere version 6.5 and greater. Builds on lower versions may work, 
but some configuration options may throw errors because they do not exist in the older versions of the vSphere API.